Description:
  TheCommentsAntispamServices: generators will copy files to install TheComments 3.0 into your App

  Usage: [bundle exec] rails g the_comments_antispam_services OPTION_NAME

# MIGRATIONS::
  > rake the_comments_antispam_services_engine:install:migrations

# This text:
  > rails g the_comments_antispam_services --help

# Moedels generators:
  > rails g the_comments_antispam_services models

  This will create:
    app/models/concerns/the_comments_antispam_services/base.rb
    app/models/concerns/the_comments_antispam_services/akismet.rb
    app/models/concerns/the_comments_antispam_services/yandex_cleanweb.rb

# Jobs generators:
  > rails g the_comments_antispam_services jobs

  This will generate:
    app/jobs/the_comments_anti_spam_job.rb

# All generators:
  > rails g the_comments_antispam_services all

  This will create:
    app/jobs/the_comments_anti_spam_job.rb
    app/models/concerns/the_comments_antispam_services/base.rb
    app/models/concerns/the_comments_antispam_services/akismet.rb
    app/models/concerns/the_comments_antispam_services/yandex_cleanweb.rb
